sub_title: Journalist/M.S. Candidate at the Columbia Journalism School
summary:
I am a journalist in their early career with a burning passion for unearthing the stories that matter. My main interests are politics, economics, social justice and education.

I have experience in print, video, and podcast.

You can check my portfolio at hummingbirdjournalism.wordpress.com
